==============================================================================
SOFTWARE COMPONENTS / SOFTWARE-KOMPONENTEN
==============================================================================

This software includes the following main components:
Diese Software umfasst die folgenden Hauptkomponenten:

Frontend:
- React.js Application
- Tailwind CSS for styling
- Modern JavaScript (ES6+)
- User Authentication
- Real-time Shopping List Management
- Product Management System
- Category Management
- Export Functionality

Backend:
- Node.js Server
- Express.js Framework
- SQLite Database
- JWT Authentication
- RESTful API
- User Management
- Admin Dashboard
- Broadcast System

Features / Funktionen:
- Multi-user shopping lists / Mehrbenutzereinkaufslisten
- Real-time synchronization / Echtzeitsynchronisation
- Category-based organization / Kategoriebasierte Organisation
- Favorite items management / Favoritenverwaltung
- Export to text files / Export in Textdateien
- Dark theme UI / Dunkles Theme
- Responsive design / Responsives Design
- Admin management tools / Admin-Verwaltungstools
- User-specific data isolation / Benutzerspezifische Datenisolierung
- UUID-based identification / UUID-basierte Identifikation

